messages.message:
Ayase: Yeek, owowow!{nl}
Don't touch the door —{nl}
your fingers stick to it.{waitkey}{clearbox}Yukino: Damn it.{nl}
It won't budge an inch.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase: Anyway, let's gather{nl}
the "Demon's Mirror Shards."{nl}
Let's trust that dandy.{waitkey}{clearbox}Yukino: Yeah, let's trust him{nl}
and head for the tower.{waitkey}{nl}
Ms. Saeko, hold on.{waitkey}{ret}
